## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mcparsedasmoperand">MCParsedAsmOperand</a> - This abstract class represents a source-level assembly instruction operand.

It should be subclassed by target-specific code. This base class is used by target-independent clients and is the interface between parsing an asm instruction and recognizing it.

Definition at line 25 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/mc/include/llvm/mc/mcparser/mcparsedasmoperand-h">MCParsedAsmOperand.h</a>.
